Basic
  Static Data Types: 
    short, int, long, char, float, double, etc.
  Control Flow: 
    if-else, while, for
  Function Definition: 
    prototype (return type, function name, parameter list), function body
  Modules
    include
  Pointers & Memory Management
    malloc, free

Advanced
